Modes(+Args):
-Off
-Constant color switch(colorA, colorB)
-Constant color fade(colorA, colorB, duration)
-Fade(color[], biColor, duration)
-Switch(color[], biColor)
-Flash(color[], lowlevel, duration)
-BiCueFlash(colorA, colorB, duration)
-Strobe(color, softRollOff, speed)

---Protocol---
Header: 24 20 1F
Field: 01-08
Payload: 00-FF (x1-x4 -> length)

---Fields(length---
01: DISPLAY_STATUS_CODE(1)
02: LIGHTING_APPLY(1) [0 => apply immediately, 1 => apply next beat]
03: LIGHTING_MODE(1)
04: LIGHTING_COLOR_SHIFT(1)
05: LIGHTING_SPEED(1)
06: LIGHTING_GENERAL_PURPOSE(2)
07: LIGHTING_PALLETTE_SIZE(1)
08: LIGHTING_PALLETTE_A(3)
09: LIGHTING_PALLETTE_B(3)
0A: LIGHTING_PALLETTE_C(3)
0B: LIGHTING_PALLETTE_D(3)
0C: LIGHTING_PALLETTE_E(3)
0D: LIGHTING_PALLETTE_F(3)
0E: LIGHTING_PALLETTE_G(3)
0F: LIGHTING_PALLETTE_H(3)


---Modes---
00: OFF()
01: SET_COLOR(PALLETTE_A boxi1Color, PALLETTE_B boxi2Color)
02: FADE_TO_COLOR(PALLETTE_A boxi1Color, PALLETTE_B boxi2Color, SPEED speed)
03: PALLETTE_FADE(PALLETTE colors, SPEED speed, LIGHTING_COLOR_SHIFT boxi2ColorIndexShift)
04: PALLETTE_SWITCH(PALLETTE colors, LIGHTING_COLOR_SHIFT boxi2ColorIndexShift)
05: PALLETTE_FLASH(PALLETTE colors, SPEED fadeOutSpeed, LIGHTING_GENERAL_PURPOSE targetBrightness, LIGHTING_COLOR_SHIFT boxi2ColorIndexShift)
06: BI_COLOR_FLASH(PALLETTE_A startColor, PALLETTE_B endColor, SPEED speed)
07: STROBE(PALLETTE_A color, SPEED frequency, GENERAL_PURPOSE rolloff)

--Status Codes---
00: BOOTING (transitions to 0x02 if host(RPI) doesn't change status code to any other status code til 12 seconds after bootup)
01: HOST_AWAKE (all good, RPI connected)
02: HOST_NO_ACTIVITY (the RPI shows no sign of activity)
03: DSP_SERVER_FAILED (shows if the display server failed to start up)
04: HOST_CONNECTION_FAILED (RPI couldn't connect to host WIFI)
05: ACTIVE (display server is running)
